<br>
1) Pound your hotkey '/pet back off'.  Your pet, if you rapidly hit this hotkey, will not fight and your enchanter can mez right off of it.<br>
<br>
2) Hit your Earthen boots hotkey.  Althou you don't like to give up your pet, it's real cheap in reagent cost and mana alike.<br>
<br>
3) If your enchanter wants to help you, (s)he will cast stun before mezzing giving you time to back off your pet.<br>
<br>
I have been working with an enchanter everyday for months, and I've learned you can fix this problem and you can also minumize this occurance too.  It takes desire on your part to make it work. <p><TABLE>
